# MERN To-Do List App

A fully functional To-Do List built with MongoDB, Express, React, and Node.js.

## Features
- ➕ Add tasks (with optional description)
- 👀 View all tasks, with All / Active / Completed filters
- ✅ Mark tasks complete via checkbox
- ✏️ Edit task title & description inline
- 🗑️ Delete tasks
- Persisted in MongoDB (Atlas or local)

